Class StringBuilderUtils

java.lang.Object
  inspiracio.lang.StringBuilderUtils

public class StringBuilderUtils
extends Object

Methods that should be in StringBuilder. We cannot extend StringBuilder, because it is final. Make static methods here.

replaceAll

public static void replaceAll(StringBuilder builder,
                              char key,

Replace all occurrences of a key-char by a value-char. Having a separate method for char-replacement is good for performance, because we know that the builder needn't grow and we will not shift chars.

Parameters:
builder - Will change this builder.
